Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.28,0:02:02.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,黛安, 现在是早上6:42.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.57,0:02:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diane, it's 6:42 a.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.12,0:02:05.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,睡得不好.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.40,0:02:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rough sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.96,0:02:10.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我刚梦见自己在吃一颗,\N大又无味的水果糖.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.24,0:02:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l had dreamt l was eating a large,\Ntasteless gumdrop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.34,0:02:12.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我醒来后才发现\N原来我在津津有味的大嚼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.61,0:02:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l awoke to realize\Nthat l was aggressively munching
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.88,0:02:15.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一粒放在枕头上的\N硅胶耳塞.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.18,0:02:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on one of my Air-Pillow\Nsilicone earplugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.01,0:02:18.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得没有一点味道.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.28,0:02:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hence the tastelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.35,0:02:23.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,大概晚餐后我应该\N早点喝咖啡.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.62,0:02:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps l should keep a closer eye\Non my after-dinner coffee consumption.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.60,0:02:29.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,肋骨那里还是疼,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.89,0:02:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Persistent soreness in the rib area,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.61,0:02:33.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在我每天早上\N坚持练15分钟瑜伽.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.90,0:02:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which l'm treating each morning with\N1 5 extra minutes of yogic discipline.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.78,0:02:38.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,练完后, 谢天谢地,\N疼痛终于撤退到我大脑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After which, thankfully,\Nthe pain retreats to a cul-de-sac
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:42.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,意识不到的遥远的\N神经死角了.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.27,0:02:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in a distant suburb\Nof my conscious mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.96,0:02:47.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的练习要开始了\N倒立.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.25,0:02:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm going to begin today\Nwith a headstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.34,0:02:58.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,黛安, 我正头着地呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.62,0:02:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diane, l am now upside down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.39,0:03:04.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,脑袋成了透气孔.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind becoming porous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.39,0:03:11.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一天的任务都浮现在眼前.\N目标越来越清晰可见.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.67,0:03:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The day's tasks coming into focus.\NObjects growing clearer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:30.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,黛安, 巨人又对了.\N我漏了东西.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.66,0:03:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diane, the Giant was right.\Nl did forget something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.66,0:04:03.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿. 还以为你在卡列斯佩尔森林\N走丢了呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Thought we'd lost you\Nto the Kalispell woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.83,0:04:07.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,2个退休女教师\N住在帕尔默家旁边.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two retired female schoolteachers\Nlive in that house next to the Palmers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:10.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她们对灰发男\N一点印象都没有.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.40,0:04:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have no memory\Nof a gray-haired man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:14.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我喝了3壶甘菊茶\N才查到的.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l had to drink three pots\Nof chamomile tea to find that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:16.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还提醒了我.\N还是等一下再说吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.57,0:04:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which reminds me.\NWould you excuse me for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.01,0:04:18.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好的.\N- 谢谢.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Sure.\N- Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.47,0:04:21.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,继续找独臂人.\N我们必须找到他.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.74,0:04:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep looking for the one-armed man.\NWe gotta find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:23.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,打搅一下, 警长,\N我想来和你道别
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.51,0:04:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, sheriff,\Nl just wanted to say goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.97,0:04:27.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,因为, 我告诉过你,\N我要去塔科马港2天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because, as you know,\Nl'm going down to Tacoma for two days
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.31,0:04:30.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,去看我姐姐格温\N和他丈夫拉利,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to visit my sister Gwen\Nand her husband, Larry,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.39,0:04:31.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们上周生了个小孩.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who had a baby last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.94,0:04:34.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 对.\N- 就是, 格温有宝宝了.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Right.\N- That is, Gwen had the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:38.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,拉利做爸爸了.\N你还记得他吗? 生了个男孩.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.22,0:04:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Larry's the father.\NYou remember? lt was a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:41.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 反正, 那个来替班\N的女孩很快就到了,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, anyway, as soon as\Nthe Can-Do temp girl gets here,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:44.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我再交代一下,电话, 咖啡\N还有对讲机都放在--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll explain the phones\Nand the coffee and the intercom--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:46.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 露西, 没问题.\N- 还有警车灯--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.33,0:04:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Lucy, it's okay.\N- And the wag--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.87,0:04:48.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会弄好的.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got it covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:51.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不是, 她应该\N马上就到了.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she should've\Nbeen here by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.42,0:04:56.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我可以等她,至少可以教教她--\N- 露西, 别担心. 快走吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.71,0:04:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l can stay and at least show her--\N- Lucy, don't worry. Just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:05:00.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有时来替班的女生不知道的.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:05:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes the Can-Do girls can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:05.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 但是, 警长--\N- 我们会照顾好的.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- But, sheriff--\N- We got it covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:10.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心, 露西.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a safe trip, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:12.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:15.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 早啊, 库.\N- 哈里.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Morning, Coop.\N- Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:17.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们今晚要\N放什么话出去?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the word\Non our delivery tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.19,0:05:19.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不需要了.\N我们准备反扑他们吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't need it.\NWe've got the jump on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:22.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道欧蕊在哪儿了.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know where Audrey is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.87,0:05:29.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你看, 病人运送起重机\N会帮助你顺利自如的移动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.14,0:05:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, the Port-O-Patient\Nwill allow you to fluently transport
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.87,0:05:31.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不幸的强生先生,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the unfortunate Mr. Johnson,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:35.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至可以在户外使用,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.15,0:05:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,allowing him to even go outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:39.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,让他坐着重新\N感受大自然.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and sit and experience\Nwhat he can of nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.96,0:05:41.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,平戈先生, 我想我表兄里欧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Pinkle, l want my cousin Leo
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.01,0:05:44.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,尽可能充分的\N再次感受生命.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to have the fullest possible\Nexperience of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:49.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对, 我就是为这个而来的.\N好, 我们再来试试这个.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.09,0:05:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's what we're here for.\NOkay, let's give it one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.14,0:05:52.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,平戈先生,\N你打算帮我安装滑道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.43,0:05:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Pinkle,\Nare you gonna install the ramp?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:55.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好, 当然, 没问题, 没问题.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.17,0:05:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sure, of course, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:05:58.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,事实上,\N我早就准备好了--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.27,0:05:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a matter of fact,\Nl already have some--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.78,0:05:59.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,夹板做的滑道--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some plywood ramp--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:03.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,松木滑槽\N我明天就帮你装. 一定.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.44,0:06:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pinewood ramp boards\Nthat l'll install tomorrow. Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.95,0:06:08.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这个建议非常好.\N现在, 我想我们可以来试试了.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a very good suggestion.\NNow, l think we are ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.79,0:06:11.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,最后. 来啦. 准备好了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally. There we go. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:17.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那儿有点小问题.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.46,0:06:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a new wrinkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:20.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真不敢相信. 它昨天还\N运作的好好的.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.99,0:06:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't believe it. lt was working\Njust so perfectly yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.71,0:06:21.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,动啊. 动啊--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Come on--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.09,0:06:24.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有时候就得对它粗暴点.\N用力撞撞它.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta be tough with this thing.\NYou gotta hit it hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.88,0:06:28.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就像对待女人一样, 在车间\N我们常这样说. 快动啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A machine is like a woman, we always\Nsay at the machine shop. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.31,0:06:34.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 波比, 你没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.57,0:06:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Bobby, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:38.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉, 能给平戈先生\N拿杯冷饮吗, 谢谢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shelly, could you get Mr. Pinkle\Na cold drink, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:40.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦我要健怡苏打.\N有那个最好.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.88,0:06:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A diet soda, please.\NThat would be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:42.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,平戈, 平戈, 平戈.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.18,0:06:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pinkle, Pinkle, Pinkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.15,0:06:46.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这简直是个死亡陷阱.\N我跟你说过我要他好好活着.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.45,0:06:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This thing is a death trap.\Nl told you we have to keep him alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.49,0:06:49.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,保险公司是有进没出\N他们不会全额赔偿的.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.75,0:06:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The insurance companies\Ndon't exactly pay off like the slots.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.58,0:06:50.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,拿了我们那份之后,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After we take our cuts,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.91,0:06:54.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就只够买这个\N或者买个一流的独轮手推车.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we had only money for this\Nor a first-rate wheelbarrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.92,0:06:58.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 太谢谢你了.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:06:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.38,0:07:00.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 非常感谢.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.67,0:07:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:02.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,波比?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobby?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.68,0:07:11.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我要去见里欧的律师了.\N- 听证会是今天, 对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.97,0:07:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l've gotta meet Leo's lawyer.\N- The hearing's today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.02,0:07:15.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,再过一会儿就好了, 老友.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be just another second, folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:18.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,波比...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobby...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.11,0:07:22.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...我们能行吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.39,0:07:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...are we okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.33,0:07:34.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哇, 好了.\N快来看看. 你看它.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's it.\NCome and take a look. You can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:36.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,运作的多顺畅.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.07,0:07:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt works just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:40.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我到外面.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come outside with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.17,0:07:44.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,让他自己弄去吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can let himself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:49.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,波比, 我们做的真棒.\N好, 够了.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.38,0:07:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobby, we're doing real good.\NOkay, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:54.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,波比?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobby?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.98,0:08:00.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,波, 波, 我够不着开关.\N波比, 我下不来了.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.26,0:08:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bob, Bob, l can't reach the switch.\NBobby, l've got a problem here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:15.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,帕尔默先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.54,0:08:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Palmer has pleaded not guilty
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:17.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不承认\N被指控为一级谋杀罪.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the charge\Nof murder in the first degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:20.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,并要求保释.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The defense has requested bail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.54,0:08:25.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是否批准保释\N将在审前听证会决定.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This pre-trial hearing is to determine\Nwhether that bail will be granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:28.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,检察官先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Prosecutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:30.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们, 代表\N华盛顿州的人民,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.16,0:08:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We, the people\Nof the State of Washington,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.09,0:08:34.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,将驳回被告的保释请求.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,move the defendant be denied bail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:36.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,其一,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the basis of one,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:39.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他被指控\N犯有极其严重的罪行.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.63,0:08:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great seriousness of the crime\Nfor which he has been accused.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.81,0:08:44.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,其二, 这明显是\N预谋的行为.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two, the apparently\Npremeditated nature of this act.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:48.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,第三, 证据表明\N帕尔默先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.77,0:08:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And three, the oft-witnessed\Ninstability of Mr. Palmer
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:52.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在他女儿死后\N情绪一直极不稳定.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,during the period\Nfollowing the death of his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:57.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,杜鲁门警长\N为辩方发言.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.21,0:08:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheriff Truman will speak\Nfor the defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:00.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,法官大人,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Honor,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.17,0:09:06.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,利兰·帕尔默\N是我们社区里广为人知,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.46,0:09:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leland Palmer\Nis a well-known, well-liked,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.55,0:09:08.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,深受爱戴, 备受尊重\N的一位成员.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,well-respected member\Nof this community.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:10.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他的祖父.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.10,0:09:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His roots go way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:13.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,约书亚·帕尔默, 带着家人,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His grandfather, Joshua Palmer,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.39,0:09:16.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,来到这里落地生根\N已有75年之久了.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.67,0:09:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,brought the family here\Nmore than 75 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:21.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,法官大人, 没人能够
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.90,0:09:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Honor, no one can know
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.94,0:09:26.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,切身体会利兰的\N丧女之痛.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.21,0:09:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what it's like to lose a daughter\Nthe way Leland did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.32,0:09:29.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,讲完了.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.62,0:09:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:32.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你, 警长.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.48,0:09:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:35.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,罗威克先生, 你是否介意...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Lodwick, would you care...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:38.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这个\N或许能在报纸上发表.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.86,0:09:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l thought l might sell this\Nto the Gazette.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.37,0:09:41.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们好像挺喜欢\N法庭素描的.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.66,0:09:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They seem to like\Ncourtroom sketches.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.58,0:09:47.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对啊, 但你为什么不\N把脸画明显些呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, why don't you try\Nfor a little more face than that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:52.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,--考虑到他在本社区的崇高地位,\N以及公众威望...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.07,0:09:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--high standing in the community,\Nand the pristine nature of his public...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.68,0:09:53.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,个人看法而已.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.26,0:09:56.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好. 谢了, 警长.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Thanks, sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.97,0:10:01.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,批准被告\N保释外出.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:10:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The defendant is released\Non his own recognizance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.19,0:10:03.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在, 利兰,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Leland,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.81,0:10:09.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,保释期间,\N不得离开本镇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as you know,\Nl will require you to remain in town
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.24,0:10:13.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,并定期\N向警长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.52,0:10:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and making your whereabouts\Nknown to the sheriff
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.99,0:10:15.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,汇报行踪.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on a regular basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:19.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,希, 查一下日历,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sid, check the calendar,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.08,0:10:22.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会尽快\N为帕尔默先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.37,0:10:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we'll set a date\Nfor Mr. Palmer's trial
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:25.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,确定终审日期.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:44.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗨.\N- 嗨.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.22,0:10:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hi.\N- Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:47.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.45,0:10:58.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 这双深邃的蓝眼睛\N今天在想些什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.73,0:10:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's behind those\Ndeep blue eyes today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.87,0:11:01.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我有个提议.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.14,0:11:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've got a proposition for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:04.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你分享我的人生.\N给你讲我的故事.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.71,0:11:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll share my life with you.\Nl'll tell it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.92,0:11:07.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,让它也成为你小说的一部分...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Part of your living novel...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.38,0:11:11.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...如果你让我看劳拉的日记.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.65,0:11:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if you let me read Laura's diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.18,0:11:17.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好狡猾哦.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.46,0:11:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's intriguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.47,0:11:24.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我读给你听吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.76,0:11:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll read it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.44,0:11:29.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但你听过的绝不能\N流出这个房间.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.73,0:11:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it mustn't physically\Nleave this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.11,0:11:32.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,可以.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Acceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.29,0:11:48.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 现在开始吗?\N- 当然.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You'll start?\N- Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.83,0:11:51.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,成交.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.12,0:11:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bargain has been struck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.79,0:12:29.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜·海沃德.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna Hayward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:43.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 来吧.\N- 好的.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Begin.\N- All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.39,0:12:46.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我来自双峰镇.\N其实, 我出生在这里.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.68,0:12:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm from Twin Peaks.\NActually, l was born here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.77,0:12:50.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸把我带到世上.\N他是个医生.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.05,0:12:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father delivered me.\NHe's a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.61,0:12:54.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那你从哪里来?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.89,0:12:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.32,0:13:00.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我在波士顿长大的.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:13:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l grew up in Boston.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.95,0:13:04.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 实际上, 我是在书中长大的.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.23,0:13:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, actually, l grew up in books.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:13.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但有些事\N你是无法从书中获得的.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.34,0:13:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's things\Nyou can't get in books.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.63,0:13:19.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,从哪儿都\N无法获得.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.91,0:13:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are things\Nyou can't get anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:24.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们才寄望\N能从他人身上获取.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we dream\Nthey can be found in other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.77,0:13:29.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,继续吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:32.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,或许真能获得.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe our dreams are real.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:40.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,轮到我了.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.77,0:13:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:43.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.37,0:13:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.03,0:13:47.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,可能,我会到屋外的\N草坪去读.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe l'll read it out here\Non the lawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:50.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别玩了.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.98,0:13:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.46,0:13:53.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们才开始啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've only just started.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:55.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那你为什么不跟着我来.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.28,0:13:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:58.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,来啊.\N有什么好怕的?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.95,0:13:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.\NWhat's there to be afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.96,0:14:00.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,快来啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.25,0:14:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:05.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,求你了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:08.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,把它还给我.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give that back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.94,0:14:17.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗德?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harold?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.65,0:14:21.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗德?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harold?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.70,0:14:24.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,太对不起了.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.98,0:14:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.95,0:14:30.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,太对不起了.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.21,0:14:40.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,请继续呈示\N证据.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.49,0:14:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The defense will continue\Nwith its evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:42.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧, 拉辛先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you would, Mr. Racine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.18,0:14:45.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以从脑电图看到,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.46,0:14:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see from these EEGs,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.51,0:14:47.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,图表在这,\N这是我的脑电波记录,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.80,0:14:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this chart here,\Nwhich is actually of my own head,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.14,0:14:50.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,它显示了\N正常的脑部活动.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.43,0:14:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is intended to show\Nnormal brain activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:53.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我反对, 法官大人\N不该使用 "正常" 这个字眼.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Objection to the use\Nof the word ''normal,'' Your Honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.69,0:14:55.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唔, 他解释的很准确.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.97,0:14:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's close enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:14:57.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,反对无效.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:14:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Objection overruled.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.32,0:15:05.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,强生先生的脑电图\N则显示了极低微的活动状态.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This chart here is of Mr. Johnson\Nand shows minimal activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.29,0:15:13.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,早前提交的\N医学报告
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.56,0:15:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A previously submitted\Nmedical report
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:17.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,陈述的很清楚\N强生先生的脑部已经严重损毁.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.59,0:15:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,states that Mr. Johnson\Nhas suffered diffuse brain damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.84,0:15:20.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,目前,他甚至\N还没能力接受
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't currently\Neven have the perspicacity
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:23.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,最基本的\N应激反应能力测试.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to take the standard CST\Ncompetency test.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.30,0:15:26.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,因此我们认为
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.57,0:15:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We therefore submit
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.97,0:15:30.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在这种情况下再继续纠缠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.24,0:15:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that trying this individual
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.14,0:15:33.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,将会成为司法系统上\N的一个莫大的笑柄.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would constitute a mockery\Nof the justice system.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.98,0:15:36.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在这个不幸的年轻人身上\N继续诉讼程序
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.25,0:15:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A proceeding that\Nthe unfortunate young man
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:39.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,将不会有任何结果.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would not even faintly comprehend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:46.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,检察官先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.22,0:15:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Prosecutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:52.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道里欧·强生\N现在的情况不是很好.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know Leo Johnson\Nisn't in very good shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.66,0:15:56.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,表面上, 坚持让他出庭\N似乎有点荒谬.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the surface, it might seem\Nridiculous to make him stand trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.62,0:16:00.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但审讯不单是\N惩罚坏人坏事.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.90,0:16:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the trial does more\Nthan just punish the wrongdoer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.67,0:16:05.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,更重要的是表达公义之声\N并对社会起警示作用,杀鸡骇猴.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.94,0:16:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt also brings a feeling of justice\Nand retribution to a community.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:08.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,作为多起罪案的\N嫌疑犯,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Among the various crimes\NLeo Johnson is suspected of,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.59,0:16:14.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这类像劳拉·帕尔默的凶案\N足以伤害到整个镇.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the murder of Laura Palmer is the sort\Nthat can wound an entire town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.35,0:16:16.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,只要里欧·强生\N还有一口气,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as Leo Johnson\Ncarries a breath,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:19.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好了.\N- 他就应出庭受审
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.42,0:16:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- All right.\N- he is as eminently deserving of a trial
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:22.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是整个社会\N共有的意识和决心!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.09,0:16:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as this community is\Nof a sense of resolution!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:24.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,够了.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.80,0:16:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.78,0:16:27.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在, 请坐, 罗威克先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.06,0:16:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, have a seat, Mr. Lodwick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.91,0:16:34.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好了, 各位\N现在可以喘口气了.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you fellas\Ncan catch your breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.29,0:16:38.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要慎重审议.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.57,0:16:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l am going to need to deliberate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.67,0:16:43.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库珀先生, 杜鲁门警长,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Cooper, Sheriff Truman,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:46.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你们能来\N一同商议.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.75,0:16:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if l could have the pleasure\Nof your company.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.51,0:16:52.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,希, 可以给我们来3杯\N黑玉空乳乳调酒吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.79,0:16:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sid, can you fix us up with three\Nblack Yukon sucker punches?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.81,0:16:54.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是的, 法官大人.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.09,0:16:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Your Honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.77,0:16:59.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,罗威克的立场很硬\N盯得很紧.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.06,0:16:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lodwick really planted his feet\Nand looked it in the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:03.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到他对谋杀指控\N那么执着.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l didn't expect him to press\Non the murder charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:07.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库珀, 里欧·强生是我们的人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cooper, is Leo Johnson our man?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:09.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 先生. 我不认为他是.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, sir. l don't believe he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.91,0:17:13.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里, 镇上的人\N有什么想法?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.18,0:17:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry, what's the temperature\Nof the town?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.12,0:17:17.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们是想公审还是处以私刑?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do they want a trial or a lynching?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.50,0:17:20.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们想要一个合适的人\N把公义带来.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They want the right man\Nbrought to justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:22.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好, 看来他们不需要马戏团.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they don't need a circus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.13,0:17:25.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而这个小瘪三,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this poor bastard,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:27.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看他也不过是颗愚妄的菜头罢了.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.99,0:17:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he seems to be a heady cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:30.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得呢, 库珀?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thoughts, Cooper?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.47,0:17:34.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得\N会抓到真凶的.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l feel the killer\Nwill eventually be apprehended.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.35,0:17:39.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你得小心点.\N他们都在打你的主意呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.63,0:17:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to watch these.\NThey sneak up on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.53,0:17:55.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我等一下就会宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm gonna declare Leo Johnson
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.08,0:17:59.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,里欧·强生不适宜出庭受审.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.36,0:17:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to be not competent to stand trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.08,0:18:04.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,鉴于其病情,\N他将被送返家中.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.36,0:18:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when medically possible,\Nthat he be shipped home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:11.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里, 你想亲口\N告诉那位小姐吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.43,0:18:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry, do you wanna tell\Nthe little lady yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.47,0:18:14.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢, 克林顿.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.74,0:18:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Clinton.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:21.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 库珀, 你来着多久了?\N- 12天了, 先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Cooper, how long you been here?\N- Twelve days, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:24.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他们不打算起诉他了.\N- 不起诉?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.42,0:18:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- They're not gonna try him.\N- No?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.77,0:18:27.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,里欧很快就可以回家了.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.05,0:18:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leo is coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.44,0:18:31.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我建议你密切留意\N那些树林.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.72,0:18:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll advise you to keep your eye\Non the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.53,0:18:35.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这里的树林很神奇...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.79,0:18:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The woods are wondrous here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.62,0:18:38.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...也奇怪.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.33,0:18:41.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.60,0:19:01.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么行李要我拿吗, 纳丁?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can l get you anything, Nadine?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:06.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你是谁?\N- 我是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.59,0:19:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Who are you?\N- Who am l?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.19,0:19:13.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你也上高中吗.\N- 对, 是的.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You go to the high school.\N- Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.41,0:19:18.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,啊, 我一下子没想起来.\N因为你不是我同班.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.70,0:19:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it took me a second.\NYou're not in any of my classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.28,0:19:20.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,去坐着吧, 甜心.\N我给你拿饮料.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.57,0:19:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you sit down, honey?\NLet me get you a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:22.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 不用, 我自己拿.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.24,0:19:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, l'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.79,0:19:27.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,爸和妈呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are Mom and Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.92,0:19:30.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 出镇去了.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.21,0:19:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, out of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.01,0:19:34.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.29,0:19:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.62,0:19:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a jack and I'm a jack\NAnd SteepIejacks are we
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.68,0:19:43.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,海沃德医生说\N是后遗症.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.96,0:19:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doc Hayward said\Nto roll with the punches.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.31,0:19:48.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算带她去\N杰柯比医生那儿吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you thought about maybe\Ntaking her to see Dr. Jacoby?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.27,0:19:52.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 他现在夏威夷\N疗养心脏病呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.53,0:19:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's in Hawaii\Nrecovering from that heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.24,0:20:00.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,它就这样掉下来了.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:20:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt just came right off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:21.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- 托吉麻辣先生要见你\N- 什么先生?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.16,0:20:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Mr. Tojamura is here.\N- Mister who?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.81,0:20:28.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.07,0:20:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.73,0:20:33.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你有预约吗, 怎么称呼...?\N- 托吉麻辣.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.01,0:20:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Do you have an appointment, Mr...?\N- Tojamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.07,0:20:38.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我代表亚洲投资银行.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.35,0:20:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l represent Asian investment bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.53,0:20:42.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,出高价
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.82,0:20:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have superior offer
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.54,0:20:46.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,购买格斯伍计划.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.82,0:20:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for Ghostwood Project.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:53.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我有东京银行\N的委托信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.86,0:20:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have commitment letters\Nfrom Tokyo banks
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.38,0:20:55.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,准备马上启动计划.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.67,0:20:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,prepared to move immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.80,0:20:58.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这些听来都非常有趣,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.07,0:20:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This all sounds very interesting,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:21:02.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但真不凑巧, 我马上有一个\N重要的电话会议要开.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.67,0:21:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but unfortunately, l have an important\Nconference call in a couple of minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.64,0:21:04.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我有计划书...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.91,0:21:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have prospectus...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.14,0:21:09.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 或许改天吧.\N- ...和诱人的.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Perhaps some other time.\N- ...and taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.61,0:21:17.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,五.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.89,0:21:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.82,0:21:21.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,百万?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Million?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.43,0:21:48.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你把这个留下.\N好让我们的人都看看.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.72,0:21:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l would like you to leave these.\NLet my people have a look at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.35,0:21:49.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,正中下怀.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.62,0:21:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Point of visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.89,0:21:53.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}谢谢, 托吉麻辣先生.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.41,0:22:08.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库珀就到了.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.67,0:22:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cooper's on his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.33,0:22:14.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}加拿大的电话, 荷恩先生.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.61,0:22:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your caII from Canada, Mr. Horne.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.25,0:22:17.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 绑匪的电话?\N- 是.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.51,0:22:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- ls that our call?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.21,0:22:19.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你来的正是时候.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.48,0:22:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You pushed it pretty close.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.22,0:22:29.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- 本杰明·荷恩.\N- 钱准备好了么?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.49,0:22:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Benjamin Horne.\N- Are you ready to pIay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.85,0:22:31.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欧蕊.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.13,0:22:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.65,0:22:35.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- 我要和我女儿讲话.\N- 等今晚吧.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.93,0:22:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l wanna talk to my daughter.\N- That can wait for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.73,0:22:38.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}一次. 越过边境,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One time. Across the border,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.28,0:22:41.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}离东大福克斯五米,\N去卡斯尔加市的那条路,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.54,0:22:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,five miIes east of Grand Forks,\Non the road to CastIegar,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.91,0:22:44.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}有一家哥伦比亚酒吧.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.17,0:22:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is a bar caIIed the CoIumbian.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.62,0:22:47.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}后面\N是一个废弃的游乐场.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.91,0:22:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behind it\Nis a faiIed amusement park.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.45,0:22:49.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}找到旋转木马.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.71,0:22:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to the merry-go-round.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.54,0:22:52.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}在一匹无头马旁\N放下公文箱,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.82,0:22:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the briefcase\Nbeside the horse with no head,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.92,0:22:55.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}午夜, 一个人.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.19,0:22:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at midnight, aIone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.92,0:22:58.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我会派人去的.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.19,0:22:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll be sending my representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.06,0:23:11.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,按你的指示,\N全是连号钞.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.33,0:23:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Serialized denominations,\Nas you instructed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.15,0:23:18.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我女儿的命就交给你了.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.44,0:23:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My daughter's life is in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.83,0:23:29.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,电话联系.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay by a phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.67,0:23:40.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,跟踪他.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.96,0:23:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.34,0:23:43.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,确保他和钱\N都要安全到达.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.60,0:23:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure that he and the money\Nare neatly delivered.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.09,0:23:48.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 把欧蕊带回来.\N- 不是库珀带她回来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.37,0:23:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Bring Audrey back.\N- Cooper's not bringing her back?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.39,0:23:51.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库珀回不来了.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.68,0:23:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cooper isn't coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.89,0:23:53.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能应付得了,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.18,0:23:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you can manage it,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.85,0:23:57.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,把欧蕊和钱箱\N都带回来.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.11,0:23:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,bring back Audrey\Nand the briefcase.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.78,0:24:08.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,5百万美金.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.06,0:24:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five million dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.58,0:24:11.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊, 真是个丰收日啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.86,0:24:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, that's a good day's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.55,0:24:22.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好,\N你进了哈罗德的公寓,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.81,0:24:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right,\Nonce you're in Harold's apartment,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.76,0:24:24.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,动作要快.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.04,0:24:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,move as fast as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.30,0:24:26.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好紧张哦.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.58,0:24:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.30,0:24:30.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,劳拉的日记就在左边书柜\N最下面的一个暗格里,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.58,0:24:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laura's diary is in a secret shelf\Nat the very bottom of the bookcase,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.39,0:24:32.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,藏在一排假书后面.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.65,0:24:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,behind a row of fake books.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.47,0:24:35.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 我想暗格的开关\N就在书柜右边
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.75,0:24:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, l think that there's a doohickey\Non the right-hand side
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.06,0:24:39.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎么地\N就可以让暗格打开.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.32,0:24:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that somehow lets the shelf\Nslide out and down.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.86,0:24:42.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,所有书都是一个样的,\N除了劳拉那本.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.13,0:24:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the notebooks look the same,\Nexcept for Laura's.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.36,0:24:44.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,红色封面的小本本.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.63,0:24:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hers is smaller with a red cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.86,0:24:46.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎么把他\N带到屋外?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.13,0:24:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you gonna get him\Nto go outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.07,0:24:48.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不去屋外,\N只是离开客厅.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.33,0:24:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not outside,\Njust out of the front room.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.82,0:24:51.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我会在窗口\N用手电给你打信号.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.10,0:24:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then l'll signal you with the flashlight\Nthrough the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.58,0:24:53.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,门会开着的.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.84,0:24:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The door will be open.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.58,0:24:56.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你喜欢这个人.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.84,0:24:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l thought you liked this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.79,0:25:00.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没错.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.08,0:25:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l do.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.22,0:25:10.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,可以了.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.49,0:25:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.26,0:25:14.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库珀递钱箱给我.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.56,0:25:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cooper hands me the briefcase.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.35,0:25:15.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我一拿就...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.63,0:25:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l take it...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.32,0:25:24.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那本·荷恩呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.60,0:25:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Ben Horne?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.23,0:25:27.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他嘛, 就放弃\N赌场的控制权.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.50,0:25:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he give up control\Nof One-Eyed Jack's.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.74,0:25:29.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你接管.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.01,0:25:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.62,0:25:31.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,把他女儿干掉?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.88,0:25:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With his daughter dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.91,0:25:35.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你啊, 爱吃牛排
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.18,0:25:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, you love a good steak
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.50,0:25:38.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,却不知道怎样把牛排\N弄到自己的碟里.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.78,0:25:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you don't want to know\Nhow it got on your plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.79,0:25:42.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你必须要学会\N怎样做交易, 布莱奇.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.08,0:25:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be serious about\Nyour business, Blackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.17,0:25:45.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那你打算怎么处置她?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.46,0:25:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you gonna do the girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.47,0:25:49.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就用这个处置啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.73,0:25:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Voila.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.98,0:26:05.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 她睡了?\N- 可香了.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.24,0:26:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Does the girl sleep?\N- Dreamland.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.24,0:26:10.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,来, 来, 来. 过来我这儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.51,0:26:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, come, come. Come to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.91,0:26:18.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩在另一房间,\N梦见鱼儿们
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.19,0:26:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ln the other room,\Nthe girl dreams of fishes
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.46,0:26:21.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗湖底的乱水草里\N游来游去.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.72,0:26:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and dark lakebeds\Nand tangle weeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.13,0:26:24.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么处理布莱奇?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.39,0:26:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Blackie?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.63,0:26:28.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我已经等够了.\N- 我们今晚来爽爽吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.90,0:26:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l've waited long enough.\N- We have our fun tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.10,0:26:35.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,吻我.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.37,0:26:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiss me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.48,0:26:41.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是. 好的. 再见.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.74,0:26:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Okay. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.07,0:26:57.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- 实验室辅助热线.\N- 噢, 我想查询检验结果.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.36,0:26:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Laboratory Services.\N- Yeah, l'm calling for some test results.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.20,0:26:59.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,海沃德医生说\N直接打给你就行了--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.46,0:26:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doc Hayward said\Nl could just call you up and--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.54,0:27:02.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- 是的, 请问哪个项目呢, 先生?\N- 哪个项目?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.80,0:27:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yes, what test was it for, sir?\N- What's it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.62,0:27:03.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}是的, 请告诉我, 先生.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.90,0:27:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, pIease, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.08,0:27:10.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是精液透析.\N姓'布伦南', 名'安迪'.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.37,0:27:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt was for a semen's analysis.\NBrennan, Andy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.05,0:27:15.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- 抱歉, 我听不清楚, 先生.\N- 哦. 布伦南, 安迪.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.31,0:27:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I'm sorry, I can't hear you, sir.\N- Sorry. Brennan, Andy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.76,0:27:19.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}哦, 透析结果是\N精液缺失, 先生.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.05,0:27:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the doctor's anaIysis\Nis oIigospermia, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.68,0:27:23.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是, 你能说慢点吗.\N我想写下来.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.95,0:27:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, could you go slower.\Nl wanna write all this down.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.44,0:27:29.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- 精液缺失.\N- "精液缺失."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.72,0:27:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- OIigospermia.\N- ''Oligospermia.''
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.86,0:27:32.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- 是的.\N- 那太可怕了.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.13,0:27:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- That's right.\N- That sounds terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.99,0:27:35.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- 我得了那个?\N- 不, 先生. 是之前.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.27,0:27:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l have that?\N- No, sir. You had that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.78,0:27:37.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 之前.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.07,0:27:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, l had it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.30,0:27:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- It means too few sperms.\N- ''Too few sperms.''
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.66,0:27:43.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- 精虫很少.\N- "精虫很少."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.96,0:27:45.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}但它们的情况很好, 先生.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.24,0:27:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.29,0:27:47.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说我好了?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.58,0:27:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean l'm cured?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.84,0:27:49.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}医生说\N它们不但能造人--{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.11,0:27:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The doctor says\Nthey're not just three men on a--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.17,0:27:54.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,"医生说\N它们不但能造人,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.45,0:27:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''Doc says they're not just\Nthree men on a fishing trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.01,0:27:57.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- 而且能造一个镇的人.\N- 而且能造一个镇的人."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.29,0:27:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- They're a whoIe damn town.\N- they're a whole damn town.''
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.60,0:28:00.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- 是的, 先生. 你理解了吗?\N- 嗯, 我理解.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.86,0:28:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- That's right, sir. Do you understand?\N- Yeah, l know what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.81,0:28:02.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就是说它们还不是真人\N但, 它们能够--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.09,0:28:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt means they're not really real\Npeople, they're--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.98,0:28:06.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- 抱歉, 先生, 我要接其他来电了.\N- 哦, 好的. 谢谢你.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.26,0:28:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I'm sorry, sir, I've got another caII.\N- Oh, okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.44,0:28:09.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- 不客气, 先生.\N- 非常感谢你.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.73,0:28:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You're weIcome, sir.\N- Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.32,0:28:13.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我能造一个镇的人!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.60,0:28:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm a whole damn town!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.49,0:28:17.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我能造一个镇的人.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.77,0:28:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm a whole damn town.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.37,0:28:25.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别问了.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.65,0:28:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.21,0:28:27.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们刚说到哪儿了?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.49,0:28:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were we?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.92,0:28:31.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好, 吧台\N和接待室在这里.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.19,0:28:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, main bar\Nand greeting room here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.21,0:28:33.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那边是赌场和贵宾室.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.49,0:28:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Casino and get-acquainted room.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.72,0:28:37.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这个呢, 布莱奇的办公室?\N- 我们到了就会知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.99,0:28:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What's this, Blackie's office?\N- We'll find out when we get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.68,0:28:45.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,独臂人在9号公路的\N'知更鸟巢'汽车旅馆呆过.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.97,0:28:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one-armed man is staying in\Nthe Robin's Nest Motel on Highway 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.52,0:28:48.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,至少一天,或一天半\N没人见过他了.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.80,0:28:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's seen him for at least\Na day, a day and a half.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.69,0:28:51.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,房间有住过的痕迹.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.97,0:28:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The room looks lived-in.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.90,0:28:53.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我找到这个.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.18,0:28:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l found this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.69,0:28:56.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,和上次的药一样.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.98,0:28:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same drug as last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.41,0:28:58.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有奇异味道, 很重 .
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.68,0:28:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A weird, deep smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.62,0:29:02.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们还在等艾伯特的分析报告.\N干得好, 豪克.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.89,0:29:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're still waiting on Albert's analysis.\NGood work, Hawk.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.16,0:29:07.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,豪克, 明早见.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.42,0:29:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hawk, see you in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.68,0:29:22.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,继续.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.94,0:29:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.77,0:29:25.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们穿过树林\N到后门去.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.04,0:29:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll approach through the woods\Nto the rear door.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.52,0:29:28.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,里面的楼梯一直\N通往工作间.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.81,0:29:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lnside are stairs leading down\Nto the working rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.44,0:29:32.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我估计,\N欧蕊就在那里.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.71,0:29:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My guess is,\Nthat's where Audrey's being held.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.32,0:29:35.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有几个打手在那儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.59,0:29:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of muscle do they have?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.70,0:29:39.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,赌场前门有2个看守,\N后门可能更多.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.95,0:29:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A couple of floor men in the casino,\Nprobably more in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.08,0:29:42.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们出发吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.36,0:29:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go get her.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.71,0:29:52.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 晚安, 安迪.\N- 明早见, 安迪.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.97,0:29:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Good night, Andy.\N- See you in the morning, Andy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.50,0:29:54.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,今天辛苦了.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.77,0:29:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.72,0:30:03.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,"格温和莱利."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.98,0:30:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''Gwen and Larry.''
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.98,0:30:15.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- 亚当人流诊所.\N- 唯, 露西在吗--? 什么?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.26,0:30:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Adam's Abortion CIinic.\N- Hi, is Lucy--? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.36,0:30:17.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}亚当人流诊所.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.63,0:30:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adam's Abortion CIinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.41,0:30:23.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗷, 我的天啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.67,0:30:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.50,0:30:34.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,能打包一杯咖啡吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.78,0:30:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can l get a cup of coffee to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.67,0:30:37.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗨.\N- 嗨.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.95,0:30:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hi.\N- Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.01,0:30:39.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你, 大杯.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.28,0:30:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Large, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.55,0:30:43.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你今天见过唐娜?\N- 没, 抱歉.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.82,0:30:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- So you seen Donna today?\N- No, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.10,0:30:45.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你呢?\N- 也没.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.39,0:30:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You?\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.02,0:30:48.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那, 买咖啡给谁?\N- 咖啡?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.29,0:30:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- So, what's with the coffee?\N- Coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.10,0:30:51.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,给利兰叔叔的.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.39,0:30:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's for Uncle Leland.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.10,0:30:54.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,家里没咖啡了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.40,0:30:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have coffee at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.40,0:30:58.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯, 我没时间聊了.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.67,0:30:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,James, l can't talk now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.57,0:31:01.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 要走了.\N- 你要走了?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.84,0:31:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l need to go.\N- You need to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.24,0:31:04.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 去哪儿?\N- 回家. 再见, 詹姆斯.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.51,0:31:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Where are you going?\N- Home. Bye, James.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.56,0:31:36.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜·海沃德.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.84,0:31:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna Hayward.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.86,0:31:42.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,3月7日, 周二.\N第二节.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.14,0:31:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,March 7th, Tuesday.\NSecond session.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.37,0:31:46.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的日记...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.65,0:31:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear diary...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.79,0:31:50.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,今天讲很久之前的事.\N好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.05,0:31:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is from a long time ago.\Nls that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.42,0:31:59.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我那时大约13岁, 可能14了.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.69,0:31:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was about 1 3 years old, 1 4 maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.17,0:32:06.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我和劳拉穿上最紧,\N最短的裙子. 紧的穿不进.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.47,0:32:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me and Laura put on our tightest,\Nshortest skirts. Too tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.89,0:32:08.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但劳拉硬帮我穿上了.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.17,0:32:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Laura talked me into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.14,0:32:15.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们去公路旅馆酒吧\N和男生约会.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.41,0:32:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were going to the Roadhouse\Nto meet boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.77,0:32:18.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们叫
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.05,0:32:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their names are
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.65,0:32:25.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,乔希, 瑞克,还有提姆.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.92,0:32:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Josh, Rick and Tim.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.62,0:32:30.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们20来岁.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.89,0:32:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're about 20 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.83,0:32:34.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对我们不错.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.10,0:32:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they're nice to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.01,0:32:48.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们觉得\N自己长大了点.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.28,0:32:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they make us feel\Nlike we're older.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.39,0:32:56.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,瑞克问我要不要去舞会.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.65,0:32:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rick asks if we wanna go party.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.48,0:32:58.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然后劳拉说, 去.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.76,0:32:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Laura says, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.40,0:33:04.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那一刻, 我有点\N迟疑了.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.66,0:33:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And all of a sudden, l feel this knot\Nbuilding up in my stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.40,0:33:08.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但劳拉已经和瑞克上车了\N我无论如何也得去.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.66,0:33:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when Laura gets in the truck\Nwith Rick, l go anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.58,0:33:12.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,树林在涌动.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.84,0:33:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stream in the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.37,0:33:15.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,满月, 我记得.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.64,0:33:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Full moon, l think.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.33,0:33:18.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,又白又亮.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.61,0:33:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's pale and light out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.59,0:33:26.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,劳拉开始围着那些男生\N跳起舞来.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.85,0:33:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laura starts to dance\Naround the boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.31,0:33:34.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她开始扭动腰肢...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.59,0:33:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She begins to move her hips...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.81,0:33:39.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...来来回回.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.09,0:33:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...back and forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.44,0:33:47.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,瑞克开始拍手, 但提姆没有\N他只是看着.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.70,0:33:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rick starts to clap, but Tim doesn't\Ndo anything, he just watches.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.16,0:33:51.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎的, 我觉得很恼怒.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.44,0:33:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, that makes me angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.62,0:33:55.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,于是我说, "我们去裸泳吧."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.88,0:33:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So l say, ''Let's go skinny-dipping.''
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.79,0:34:03.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们脱光了衣服.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.09,0:34:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We take off our clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.59,0:34:07.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道那些男生在看着.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.86,0:34:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know the boys are watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.13,0:34:11.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,劳拉开始和乔希,瑞克接吻.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.39,0:34:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laura starts to kiss Josh and Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.97,0:34:13.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而我却不知所措.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.23,0:34:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.89,0:34:17.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我游开了.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.17,0:34:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So l swim away.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.44,0:34:23.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得自己想逃离, 但我没有.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.71,0:34:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l feel like l wanna run, but l don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.57,0:34:28.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这时,提姆游了过来.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.85,0:34:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tim swims out to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.28,0:34:34.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他先吻了我的手...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.55,0:34:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He kisses my hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.75,0:34:38.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,...接着吻唇.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.02,0:34:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and then me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.80,0:34:48.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那感觉至今还在.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.06,0:34:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can still feel that kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.01,0:34:55.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他的双唇又暖又甜.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.27,0:34:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His lips are warm and sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.93,0:35:00.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我的心猛跳.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.21,0:35:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart jumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.19,0:35:05.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他说什么,\N我都听不清了.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.45,0:35:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's talking to me,\Nbut l can't hear him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.74,0:35:09.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,只有吻.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.02,0:35:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.20,0:35:15.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,后来再也没见过他了.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.46,0:35:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l never saw him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.95,0:35:19.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我的初恋.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.23,0:35:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt was the first time l ever fell in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.88,0:35:29.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就这些了.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.17,0:35:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.05,0:35:32.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,太美了, 唐娜.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.31,0:35:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was beautiful, Donna.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.63,0:36:11.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我来对付他.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.91,0:36:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.91,0:37:21.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.18,0:37:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.99,0:37:58.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在这等, 哈里.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.26,0:37:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait here, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.91,0:38:05.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不通. 死路.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.20,0:38:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.97,0:38:25.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 2个人.\N- 欧蕊呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.25,0:38:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Two.\N- Audrey?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.78,0:38:42.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,仔细想想,\N还不赖嘛.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.06,0:38:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not such a bad way to go,\Nall things considered.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.28,0:38:45.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不赖, 不赖. 计划完美.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.57,0:38:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. lt's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.29,0:38:49.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 她一个人?\N- 南希在.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.57,0:38:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- ls she alone?\N- Nancy's with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.92,0:38:53.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么是她能为你做而我不能?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.17,0:38:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does she do for you l can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.55,0:38:56.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 新鲜感.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.81,0:38:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, something new.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.57,0:39:19.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,很多人以为兰花要生长在\N国外潮湿的地方.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.83,0:39:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most people imagine orchids\Ngrowing in exotic, steamy places.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.20,0:39:20.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,其实哪里都可以种.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.47,0:39:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can grow them anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.99,0:39:23.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,主要是水分\N和阳光, 不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.27,0:39:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's all basically a matter\Nof water and light, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.12,0:39:26.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真美.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.41,0:39:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.66,0:39:29.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这儿, 看.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.95,0:39:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.50,0:39:37.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗, 湿度最重要.\N嗯, 我是说, 是湿度的控制.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.78,0:39:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, humidity is paramount.\NWell, the control of it, l mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.51,0:39:40.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,太湿\N容易病.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.79,0:39:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too much moisture\Nis an invitation to disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.47,0:39:44.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,3个萼片和3个花瓣.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.73,0:39:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three sepals and three petals.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.60,0:39:48.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,底部的花瓣,\N因为长得像下唇,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.86,0:39:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bottom petal,\Nshaped like a lower lip,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.31,0:39:50.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,所以叫唇瓣.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.57,0:39:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is called a labellum.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.48,0:39:53.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好精致.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.74,0:39:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So delicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.40,0:40:01.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 其实是个月台,\N真的, 为了让昆虫降落授粉.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.67,0:40:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's the landing platform,\Nreally, for pollinating insects.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.86,0:40:04.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真浪漫, 是吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.15,0:40:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Romantic, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.44,0:40:38.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,恕我失陪一会儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.71,0:40:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you excuse me a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.19,0:41:15.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你好.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.45,0:41:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.06,0:41:19.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,可以带我去见\N欧蕊·荷恩, 劳驾了?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.32,0:41:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you take me\Nto Audrey Horne, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.73,0:41:23.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 她不在.\N- 那我们再去看看吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.02,0:41:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l don't think she's available.\N- Let's double-check.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.05,0:41:46.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是我的主意, 好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.31,0:41:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's not my idea, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.84,0:41:49.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对他们\N你只是砧板上的一块肉.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.12,0:41:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're nothing but meat on a hook\Nto these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.39,0:41:50.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.65,0:41:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.68,0:41:55.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欧蕊, 能听见我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.96,0:41:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audrey, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.95,0:42:07.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我的祈祷.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.20,0:42:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.78,0:42:11.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欧蕊, 我现在要\N带你离开这里了.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.07,0:42:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audrey, l'm gonna take you\Nout of here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.14,0:42:33.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.40,0:42:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.10,0:42:38.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,和我吻别.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.37,0:42:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you leave me with a kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.77,0:42:42.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你还是老样子,\N很好.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.04,0:42:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the way you want it,\Nthat's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.78,0:43:26.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,把枪放下.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.05,0:43:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drop the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.82,0:43:29.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,慢点放.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.09,0:43:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.45,0:43:36.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在, 转过身去.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.72,0:43:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.93,0:43:55.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,幸好你们\N藏不住秘密.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.21,0:43:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing you guys\Ncan't keep a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.10,0:44:00.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,投得好.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.38,0:44:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good throw.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.61,0:44:12.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,发生了枪战.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.90,0:44:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's been gunfire.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.53,0:44:15.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,杜鲁门和库珀\N带着你女儿走了.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.80,0:44:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truman and Cooper are leaving\Nwith your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.58,0:44:21.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看看, 你是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.83,0:44:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, who can this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.88,0:44:25.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,罗威克先生. 检察官办事处, 嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.14,0:44:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monsieur Lodwick. DA's office, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.94,0:44:45.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 怎么了?\N- 没事.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.23,0:44:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- ls something wrong?\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.27,0:44:46.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你吓了我一大跳, 这样而已.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.53,0:44:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just frightened me, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.20,0:44:55.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,来这边.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.47,0:44:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.16,0:44:58.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,给我讲讲这个兰花. 这棵.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.44,0:44:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me about this orchid. This one.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.05,0:45:17.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗德, 不, 你不明白.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.33,0:45:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harold, no, you don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.14,0:45:24.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,马蒂!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.40,0:45:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.19,0:45:28.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.47,0:45:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.28,0:45:35.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在找秘密吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.54,0:45:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you looking for secrets?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.37,0:45:39.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,全都只是为了那个吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.65,0:45:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls that what all this is about?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.08,0:45:44.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好, 或许我能帮助你们.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.35,0:45:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe l can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.38,0:45:49.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你们想知道\N终极秘密是什么吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.66,0:45:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know\Nwhat the ultimate secret is?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.80,0:45:51.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你们想知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.06,0:45:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.47,0:45:54.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,劳拉知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.73,0:45:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laura did.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.56,0:46:03.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,知道是谁杀了你.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.84,0:46:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The secret of knowing who killed you.
